            <div type="bibliography">
                
            </div>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>This list of three miracles of Yāred reflects the number of miracles attested in <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient12860">London, British Library, BL Oriental 12860</ref>.
                    However, since this manuscript is incomplete, the number of miracles attributed to Yāred is probably higher. Incipits are taken 
                    from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">87</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Satan">
                    <label>Miracle of overcoming of Satan by Yāred</label>
                    <q xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="lost"/>ወእምድኅረ፡ አዕረፈ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10245Yared">ያሬድ፡</persName> ካህን፡ ፈጺሞ፡ 
                        ገድሉ፡ ወመዊዖ፡ ሰይጣነ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Decoration">
                    <label>The miracle of Yāred, when decoration of the church was hidden from him</label>
                    <q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ነገር፡ በእንተ፡ ሰዋሬሁ፡ ለያሬድ፡ ካህን፡ ሠርጐ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Gift">
                    <label>The miracle of Yāred, when a gift dedicated to him was hidden from him</label>
                    <q xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ነገር፡ በእንተ፡ ሰዋሬሁ፡ ለያሬድ፡ ካህን፡ ዘተወህቦ፡ ጸጋ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
